{"about_the_game":"An atmospheric experience putting you back where the previous events left off in the first game of the series. Now focused around a little girl Sophie, her world is consumed when a strange board game catches her attention in a toy store.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/extras/TrainRide.gif?t=1706625338\" /><br><br>Play a horror board game, rolling the dice and exploring each part of it with new gameplay, puzzles, vivid and surreal environments and the creepy clown Vasilus stalking you and leading you into the Cave of Illusions. Explore Quirky Quacker Love Tunnel, Giddy-up Carousel, Hippity Hop Hut, Tip-Toe Treat Trail, Titter Toy Store, Shenanigan Shingles and finally Cave of Illusions.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/extras/CardNew.gif?t=1706625338\" /><br><br>Vasilus plays with you not only using dice, but cards as well, inside each part of the board game he gives you a useful special card that helps you get through the level, but sometimes it also helps Vasilus too. Please enjoy the very unique, diverse and creepy board game - Cave of Illusions: Twistyland!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/extras/GirlTurnSwirl.gif?t=1706625338\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/extras/Board1.gif?t=1706625338\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1706625338","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/page.bg.jpg?t=1706625338","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1706625338","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/